PlaceIQ 

PlaceIQ is a cutting-edge, client-side Placement Intelligence Platform built by Ritesh Kumar Singh. It empowers students to discover 500+ colleges, predict CTCs/placement probabilities, forecast GATE/CAT scores, compare institutions head-to-head, and track weekly news—all in a sleek, interactive web app.
​

✨ Key Features
College Discovery: Filter/search 500 colleges by stream, state, fees, NIRF rank, avg CTC (e.g., IIT Bombay: 24.5L avg).
​

AI Placement Predictor: Input CGPA, tier, skills (Python/ML/Docker), internships → Get CTC range + probability (95% accuracy claimed).
​

Score Oracle: Predict GATE/CAT/CUET scores from mocks, prep months, subjects → Eligibility ranks (e.g., GATE CSE 65+ for IISc).
​

Head-to-Head Compare: Stack 4 colleges; neon highlights best metrics (placement %, highest offers).
​

Weekly Digest: Curated news (e.g., IITs record CTCs, AI hiring surge 62% MoM).
​

Dark/Light Theme + Animations: Custom cursor, orbs, shimmers, tilt effects for immersive UX.
​

🚀 Quick Start
Open placeiq-v4.html in any modern browser (Chrome/Firefox).

Register/login (demo: any email/password).

Navigate tabs: Colleges → Predict → Compare → News.

All data client-side—no servers, zero tracking.
​

🛠 Tech Stack
Frontend: Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS (Exo2, DM Mono, Outfit fonts).

Effects: Canvas grids/noise/orbs, CSS animations (shimmers, tilts, marquees).

AI Models: Rule-based predictors (CGPA/skills weighted formulas).
​

📱 Responsive & Offline
Fully responsive (mobile/desktop). Runs offline post-load. Quick tour on first login.
